    "Title": {},
    "Content": {
      "en": "<div class=\"sc-detail-risk-matrix\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-scale-balanced\"></i></div><div><h3>Regulatory Volatility</h3><p>Frequent changes in customs rules require constant interpretation and operational alignment.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-barcode\"></i></div><div><h3>HS Classification & Valuation Risk</h3><p>Incorrect codes or declared values can create duty exposure, penalties and shipment holds.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-hourglass-half\"></i></div><div><h3>Inspection Bottlenecks</h3><p>Unexpected checks and documentation gaps can slow release and increase port-side costs.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-file-circle-check\"></i></div><div><h3>Post-Clearance Audit Exposure</h3><p>Records, licensing and supporting evidence must remain audit-ready after cargo release.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-building-columns\"></i></div><div><h3>Local Enforcement Variability</h3><p>Different ports and authorities can apply requirements with local procedural differences.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-database\"></i></div><div><h3>Data Integrity Failure</h3><p>Inconsistent shipment data across systems and documents increases compliance risk.</p></div></div></div>",
      "vi": "<div class=\"sc-detail-risk-matrix\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-scale-balanced\"></i></div><div><h3>Regulatory Volatility</h3><p>Frequent changes in customs rules require constant interpretation and operational alignment.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-barcode\"></i></div><div><h3>HS Classification & Valuation Risk</h3><p>Incorrect codes or declared values can create duty exposure, penalties and shipment holds.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-hourglass-half\"></i></div><div><h3>Inspection Bottlenecks</h3><p>Unexpected checks and documentation gaps can slow release and increase port-side costs.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-file-circle-check\"></i></div><div><h3>Post-Clearance Audit Exposure</h3><p>Records, licensing and supporting evidence must remain audit-ready after cargo release.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-building-columns\"></i></div><div><h3>Local Enforcement Variability</h3><p>Different ports and authorities can apply requirements with local procedural differences.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-database\"></i></div><div><h3>Data Integrity Failure</h3><p>Inconsistent shipment data across systems and documents increases compliance risk.</p></div></div></div>",
      "cn": "<div class=\"sc-detail-risk-matrix\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-scale-balanced\"></i></div><div><h3>Regulatory Volatility</h3><p>Frequent changes in customs rules require constant interpretation and operational alignment.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-barcode\"></i></div><div><h3>HS Classification & Valuation Risk</h3><p>Incorrect codes or declared values can create duty exposure, penalties and shipment holds.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-hourglass-half\"></i></div><div><h3>Inspection Bottlenecks</h3><p>Unexpected checks and documentation gaps can slow release and increase port-side costs.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-file-circle-check\"></i></div><div><h3>Post-Clearance Audit Exposure</h3><p>Records, licensing and supporting evidence must remain audit-ready after cargo release.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-building-columns\"></i></div><div><h3>Local Enforcement Variability</h3><p>Different ports and authorities can apply requirements with local procedural differences.</p></div></div><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-card\"><div class=\"sc-detail-risk-icon\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-database\"></i></div><div><h3>Data Integrity Failure</h3><p>Inconsistent shipment data across systems and documents increases compliance risk.</p></div></div></div>"
